Package: podman-docker
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, podman
Conflicts: docker.io, docker-ce, docker-ce-cli
Provides: docker
Description: Emulate Docker CLI using Podman
 This package provides a Docker CLI compatibility layer using
 Podman. It installs a /usr/bin/docker script that calls podman,
 sets up DOCKER_HOST environment variable, creates a docker.sock
 symlink to podman.sock, and provides docker-* man pages.
